            <script>
              document.getElementById('basicsModal5-content1').innerHTML =
                marked('Today more than ever before, we are surrounded by systems, both formal and informal, that define the quality of our lives. We encounter them in our workplaces, in our homes, on our vacations, and within our families. We encounter them from the moment we wake to the moment we sleep, and their pervasive nature steers the courses of our lives.');
